      "text": [
        "2069 - وَ فِي خَبَرٍ آخَرَ قَالَ: «لاَ بَأْسَ بِأَنْ تَدْفَعَ عَنْ نَفْسِكَ وَ عَنْ مَنْ تَعُولُ إِلَى وَاحِدٍ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2069 - In another narration, it is said:\n\"There is no harm in giving Zakat al-Fitr for yourself and those you support to a single recipient.\""
        ]
      }
    }
  },
